For a further bonus, such as for strategic or institutional investors, please directly contact kumar@namahe.io  Quote from: earthcoin on June 18, 2018, 07:43:26 PM What would you say is the biggest advantage of using blockchain for this?  Blockchain allows us to make supply chains truly transparent and inalterable. Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: ⭐⭐ [ANN][TOKEN SALE] Namahe - First supply chain based on blockchain and A.I. ⭐⭐
Body: First Socially Responsible Supply Chain Based Blockchain Platform Namahe To Add AI Layer for Accountability  Namahe is a fintech startup that is bringing supply chain and resultant audits for transparency to the blockchain. By leveraging on the immutable nature of the technology, the company gives the users the ability to tag their products, from manufacturing level, right down to the sales store it is placed in. This allows customers (and any stakeholder, for that matter), to verify that the product and its materials are acquired in an ethical manner.  Brands and companies that will adopt transparency and self audits through Namahe will show full transparent nature of their business, increase their image, avoid negative publicity, increase customer loyalty and save money on audits.  Read the details in the article of Coinidol dot com, the world blockchain news outlet: https://coinidol.com/first-socially-responsible-supply-chain-based-blockchain-platform/

Author: Parodium
Title: ⭐⭐ [ANN][TOKEN SALE] Namahe - First supply chain based on blockchain and A.I. ⭐⭐
Body: [Disclaimer] Please note that this thread is launched on behalf of the Namahe project. Further information can be obtained by e-mailing: info@namahe.io. I am the community manager of Namahe. -------------------------   A leap forward to a sustainable future.  Globalisation has had a positive impact in creating a single worldwide marketplace where buyers and sellers can trade goods and services easily.  However, transparency across value chains has always been insufficient. As a result there are inefficiencies & risks of exploitation lower down the supply chain. This can include wage exploitation, child labour, poor working conditions and human rights violations, especially towards women.  Introducing Namahe, the First Socially Responsible Supply chain based on blockchain and artificial intelligence. Namahe will allow full transparency throughout the supply chain by decentralizing the data using Blockchain and providing a common platform for information sharing by all stakeholders involved. This will help reduce exploitation by creating tools and interfaces for each tier and empowering all stakeholders through the use of blockchain.  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- Executive Summary ------------------------- Whitepaper ------------------------- Team Page -------------------------  Website | Telegram | Medium | Youtube | LinkedIn | Facebook | Twitter | Reddit | Instagram   Token Sale Details;  Whitelisting (includes KYC & AML) for the token sale opens Monday 7th of May, 00:00 AM UTC Time - Soft Cap: 4,000,000 USD - Hard Cap: 30,000,000 USD - Minimum Investment: 0.25 ETH - Maximum Investment: 200 ETH    ------------------------- Website | Telegram | Medium | Youtube | LinkedIn | Facebook | Twitter | Reddit | Instagram

Body: Thanks for the kind words. We think that our solution offers a great chance to improve an industry that has been neglected for a long time. By producing a transparent and sustainable platform where all the different parts of the supply chain and interact and work together, we hope to inspire change in the industry and believe that our partners will benefit from this change too.
